A vintage sepia-toned photograph of an old European butcher shop counter from the early 1900s, featuring an ornate brass cash register with an unfurling paper receipt, surrounded by hanging sausages of various sizes and shapes, antique meat hooks, and a weathered wooden cutting board with a cleaver, dramatic warm lighting from a single dusty window casting long shadows across worn marble countertops, nostalgic atmosphere with rich brown and amber tones.
